📁 What Each Folder Does
🔹 pages/

Full screens (one route = one folder)

Example:

/upload → UploadPortfolio.jsx

🔹 components/

Reusable UI blocks

Button
Card
Navbar
Charts


No business logic.

🔹 services/

All API calls

fetch portfolio
send investment input


No UI code.

🔹 hooks/

Reusable logic

useFetch
useSession
useDebounce

🔹 context/

Global app state

session id
portfolio data
allocation data

🔹 routes/

All route definitions

🔹 utils/

Helper functions & constants